Concessional funding in addition to
Uganda govt’s $700m equity financing, Finance Ministry says in
budget document handed to reporters in capital, Kampala.
*Document doesn’t provide credit terms
*Construction of 600MW hydropower plant to start before yr-end:
ministry
*NOTE: Construction of country’s biggest energy project delayed
for 1 yr because of procurement irregularities
*NOTE: China International Water and Electric, Sinohydro,
Italy’s Salini Costruttori, Iran’s Perlite Construction, and
